title: Skylark Pharmacy
name: Of_ Ade
text:
A trust pharmacy that was the biggest in Abuja in the early days.
They have numerous branches scattered round Abuja and have a good stock of drugs.
They now have supermarkets in their stores alongside the Pharmacy.
The good thing is if a drug isnâ€™t available in one location, they can point you to another location that has the drug in-store.

title: Skylark Pharmacy
name: Idoko Joseph
text: This is one of best pharmacy wholesale who deals on original products of  medicines of all kind. Their prices are also affordable wise and you can trust any product of buys from them due to conducive and low temperature storage which one standard way of storing drugs. We have been patronising this very place for more 6yrs and they are reliable. Please pay visit if you want good pharmacy products for shop.

title: Skylark Pharmacy
name: Ahmed Ademola Olugbile
text: A 2r HR pharmacy with other branches within AMAC I have witnessed and been to. It has wheelchair accessible entrance and has a security on point. It boasts of a wide variety of drugs available in capsules, syrups and also some daily health consumptions. It's a moderately priced pharmacy.
